hadiths[85]{hadithnumber,text}:
4978,"mujh ko Aaisha, Abdullah aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein das saal rahe aur Quran nazil hota raha aur Madina mein bhi das saal tak rahe aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahan bhi Quran nazil hota raha."
4979,"mujh ko Aaisha, Abdullah aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein das saal rahe aur Quran nazil hota raha aur Madina mein bhi das saal tak rahe aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahan bhi Quran nazil hota raha."
4980,"mujhey malum hua hai ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baat karne lagey. us waqt Ummul-Momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) aap ke paas maujood thin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha ke janti ho ye kon hain? ya isi tarah ke alfaz Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaaey. Ummul-Momenin ne kaha ke Dahiya Kalbi hain. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya : Allah ki qism ! us waqt ( tak) bhi mein unhein Dahiya Kalbi samajhtii rahi. aakhir jab maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khutba suna jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ke aaney ki khabar sunai tab mujhey haal malum hua ya isi tarah ke alfaz bayan kiye. Motamir ne bayan kya ke mere walid (Sulaimaan) ne kaha, maine abu-Usman Mehdi se kaha ke aap ne ye hadis kisse suni thi? unhon-ne bataya ke Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se."
4981,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har Nabi ko aisey aisey moa'jazaat ata kiye gaey ke (unhein dekh kar log) un par eman laey (ba'd ke zamaney mein unka koi asar nahi raha) aur mujhey jo moa'jza diya gaya hai wo wahi (Qur'aan) hai jo Allah Taala ne mujh par nazil ki hai. (iska asar qiyamat tak baqi rahega) isliye mujhey ummeed hai ke qiyamat ke din mere taabea' farman log doosrey paighambaron ke taabea' farmaanon se zyada hongey.
4982,Allah Taala Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par pai-dar-pai wahi utaartaa raha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke qaribi zamaney main to bahut wahi utri phir iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee.
4983,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar padey aur aik ya 2 raaton main (tahajjud ki Namaz ke liye) na uth sakey to aik aurat (Aura binte-rab abu-Lahab ki joroo) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aai aur kehney lagi Muhammad ! mera khayal hai ke tumharey shaitan ne tumhen chhod diya hai. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki ( والضحى * والليل إذا سجى * ما ودعك ربك وما قلى‏ ) ''qasam hai din ki roshni ki aur raat ki jab wo qarar pakdey ke aap ke parwardigar ne na aapko chhoda hai aur na wo aap se khafa hua hai.''
4984,"Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Zaid-bin-Saabit, Saeed-bin-Aas, Abdullaah-bin-Zubair, Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Haaris-bin-Hishaam (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke Quran Majeed ko kitabi shakl mein likhein aur farmaya ke agar Quran ke kisi muhaawrey main tumhara Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se ikhtilaf ho to us lafz ko Quraish ke muhaaware ke mutabiq likho, kyonke Quran un hi ke muhaawrey par nazil hua hai chunanche unhon-ne aisa hi kya."
4985,"kash! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us waqt dekhta jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil hoti ho. chunanche jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maqam Jaarana mein thahrey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke uper kapdey se saaya kar diya gaya tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aap ke chand sahaba maujood they ke aik shakhs ke barey mein kya fatwa hai. jisne khushbu mein basaa hua aik jubba pahan kar ehram baandha ho. thodi der ke liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha aur phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi aana shuru ho gaee. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Yala ko ishaare se bulaya. Yala aaey aur apna sar (is kapdey ke jis se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye saaya kya gaya tha) andar kar liya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra us waqt surkh ho raha tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tezi se saans ley rahe they, thodi der tak yahi kaifiyat rahi. phir ye kaifiyat door ho gaee aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke jisne abhi mujh se Umre ke mutaalliq fatwa puchha tha wo kahan hai? us shakhs ko talash karke aap ke paas laya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke jo khushbu tumharey badan ya kapdey par lagi hui hai usko teen martaba dho lo aur jubbe ko utaar do phir Umre mein bhi isi tarah karo jis tarah Haj mein kartey ho."
4986,"jange-Yamaama main (sahaaba ki bahut badi tadaad ke) Shahid ho janey ke baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bula bhejaa. us waqt umr (Raziallahu anhu) mere paas aaey aur unhon-ne kaha ke yamaama ki jang mein bahut badi tadaad mein Quran ke qaariyon ki shahadat ho gaee hai aur mujhey dar hai ke isi tarah kuffaar ke sath dusri jangon mein bhi Quran ke qaariyon ki badi tadaad mein qatl ho jaeinge aur yun Quran ke jaanney walon ki bahut badi tadaad khatm ho jaeygi. isliye mera khayal hai ke aap Quran Majeed ko (baa-qaayda kitabi shakl mein) jama karne ka hukm de dein. maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke aap aik aisa kaam kis tarah karengey jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apni zindagi mein) nahi kiya? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska ye jawab diya ke Allah ki qasam! ye to aik kaare-khair hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ye baat mujh se baar-baar kehtey rahe. aakhir Allah Taala ne is mas'ale mein mera bhi Sina khol diya aur ab meri bhi wahi raey ho gaee jo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki thi. Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aap (Zaid (rz)) jawan aur aqlmand hain, aapko kisi mamley mein muttahim bhi nahi kya ja sakta aur aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wahi likhtey bhi they, isliye aap Quran Majeed ko poori talash aur mehnat ke sath aik jagah jama kar dein. Allah ki qism ! agar ye log mujhey kisi pahaad ko bhi uski jagah se dusri jagah hataaney ke liye kehtey to mere liye ye kaam itna mushkil nahi tha jitna ke unka ye hukm ke main Quran Majeed ko jama kar dun. maine is par kaha ke aap log aik aisey kaam ko karne ki himmat kaisey kartey hain jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud nahi kya tha. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ye aik amal khair hai. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ye jumla barabar dohraatey rahe, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne mera bhi unki aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki tarah Sina khol diya. chunanche maine Quran Majeed (jo mukhtalif chizon par likha hua maujood tha) ki talash shuru kar di aur Quran Majeed ko khajoor ki chhilii hui shaakhon, patley pattharon se, (jin par Quran Majeed likha gaya tha) aur logon ke seenon ki madad se jama karne laga. sura Tauba ki aakhiri aayatein mujhey abu-Khuzaima Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas likhi hui miliin, ye chand aayatein maktoob shakl mein unke siwa aur kisi ke paas nahi thiin لقد جاءكم رسول من أنفسكم عزيز عليه ما عنتم‏  se sura tauba ke khaatme tak. jama ke baad Quran Majeed ke ye saheefey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas mehfooz they. phir unki wafat ke baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne jab tak wo zinda rahe apne sath rakha phir wo Ummul-Momenin Hafsa-binte-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas mehfooz rahe."
4987,"Huzaifa-bin-Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) ameerul-momineen Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey us waqt Usman (Raziallahu anhu) Armeeniya aur Aazrbaijaan ki fateh ke silsiley mein Sham (Syria) ke ghaaziyon ke liye jang ki taiyaariyon mein masroof they, taake wo Iraq walon ko sath lekar jang karein. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) Quran Majeed ki qirat ke ikhtilaf ki wjah se bahut pareshan they. aap ne Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke ameerul-momineen is se pahley ke ye ummat (ummate-muslima) bhi yahudiyon aur nasraaniyon ki tarah kitabullah mein ikhtilaf karne lagey, aap uski khabar lijiye. chunanche Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan kahlaayaa ke saheefey (jinhein Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke hukm se jama kya tha aur jin par mukammal Quran Majeed likha hua tha) hamein de dein taake ham unhi mushafon main (kitaabii shakl mein) naql karwaa lein. phir asl ham aapko lota dengey Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne wo saheefey Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bhej diye aur aap ne Zaid-bin-Saabit, Abdullaah-bin-Zubair, Sad bin -Aas, Abdur-Rehman bin Haris-bin-Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke wo un saheefon ko mushafon mein naql kar lein. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne us jamat ke teen qureshi sahaabiyon se kaha ke agar aap logon ka Quran Majeed ke kisi lafz ke silsiley mein Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se ikhtilaf ho to usey Quraish hi ki zaban ke mutabiq likh lein kyonke Quran Majeed bhi Quraish hi ki zaban mein nazil hua tha. chunanche un logon ne aisa hi kya aur jab tamam saheefey mukhtalif nuskhon mein naql kar liye gaey to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne un saheefon ko wapas lota diya aur apni saltanat ke har ilaqe mein naql shuda musahaf ka eik-eik nuskha bhijwaa diya aur hukm diya ke iske siwa koi cheez agar Quran ki taraf mansub ki jati hai chahe wo kisi saheefe ya musahaf mein ho to usey jalaa diya jaey."
4988,"jab ham (Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamane mein) musahaf ki sura mein Quran Majeed ko naql kar rahe they, to mujhey sura Ahzaab ki aik aayat nahi mili halanke main us aayat ko bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna karta tha aur aap uski tilawat kya kartey they, phir ham ne usey talash kya to wo Khuzaima bin Sabit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas mili . wo aayat ye thii من المؤمنين رجال صدقوا ما عاهدوا الله عليه‏ chunaanche ham ne us aayat ko sura Ahzaab mein laga diya."
4989,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne zamaanae-khilaafat mein mujhey bulaya aur kaha ke tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney Quran likhtey they. isliye ab bhi Quran (jama karne ke liye) tum hi talash karo. maine talash ki aur sura Tauba ki aakhiri 2 aayatein mujhey Khuzaima Ansari ke paas likhi hui miliin, unke siwa aur kahin ye 2 aayatein nahi mil rahi thin. wo aayatein ye thiin لقد جاءكم رسول من أنفسكم عزيز عليه ما عنتم aakhir tak."
4990,"jab aayat لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين والمجاهدون في سبيل الله‏ naazil hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Zaid ko mere paas bulao aur unse kaho ke takhtii, dawaat aur mundhey ki haddi (likhney ka saamaan) lekar aaiin, ya rawi ne uski bajaey haddi aur dawaat (kahaa) phir (jab wo aagey to) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke likho لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين والمجاهدون في سبيل الله‏ nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Amr ibn-Umme-Maktoom baithey huey they jo naa-beenaa they, unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! phir aap ka mere barey mein kya hukm hai. main to naa-beenaa hun (jihad mein nahi ja sakta ab mujh ko bhi mujaahideen ka darja milega ya nahin) us waqt ye aayat yun utrii لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين والمجاهدون في سبيل الله‏naazil hui."
4991,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne mujh ko (pahley ( Arab ke aik hi muhaawrey par Quran padhaayaa. maine unse kaha (is mein bahut sakhti hogi) mein barabar unse kehta raha ke aur muhaawaron mein bhi padhney ki ijazat do. yahan tak ke saat (7) muhaawaron ki ijazat milii.
4992,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein, maine Hisham-bin-Hakeem ko sura furqan Namaz mein padhtey suna, maine unki qirat ko ghaur se suna to malum hua ke wo sura mein aisey huroof padh rahe hain ke mujhey is tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi padhaayaa tha, qareeb tha ke main unka sar Namaz hi mein pakad leta lekin maine badi mushkil se sabr kya aur jab unhon-ne salam phera to maine unki chadar se unki gardan baandh kar puchha ye sura jo maine abhi tumhen padhtey huey suni hai, tumhen kis ne is tarah padhai hai? unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey isi tarah padhai hai, maine kaha tum jhoot boltey ho. khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey is se mukhtalif doosrey harfon se padhai jis tarah tum padh rahe they. aakhir mein unhein kheenchtaa hua Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke maine us shakhs se sura furqan aisey harfon mein padhtey suni jinki aap ne mujhey taleem nahi di hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) tum pahley unhein chhod do aur aey Hisham ! tum padh ke sunao. unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney bhi un hi harfon mein padha jin mein maine unhein Namaz mein padhtey suna tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sun kar farmaya ke ye sura isi tarah nazil hui hai. phir farmaya umr ! ab tum padh kar sunao maine is tarah padha jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey taleem di thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey bhi sun kar farmaya ke isi tarah nazil hui hai. ye Quran saat (7) harfon par nazil hua hai to tumhen jis tarah aasan ho padho."
4993,"mein Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke aik iraaqii unke paas aaya aur puchha ke kafan kaisa hona chahiye ? Ummul-Momenin ne kaha : afsos us se matlab ! kisi tarah ka bhi kafan ho tujhey kya nuqsan hoga. phir us shakhs ne kaha Ummul-Momenin mujhey apne musahaf dikhaa dijiye. unhon-ne kaha kyon ? (kya zarurat hai) usne kaha taake main bhi Quran Majeed us tarteeb ke mutabiq padhun kyonke log baghair tarteeb ke padhtey hain. unhon-ne kaha phir usmein kya qabahat hai jaun-sii sura to chahey pahley padh ley ( jaun-sii sura chahey baad mein padh ley agar utarney ki tarteeb dekhta hai) to pahley mufassal ki aik sura , utrii (اقرا باسم ربك) jis mein jannat w dozakh ka zikr hai. jab logon ka dil Islam ki taraf rujoo ho gaya ( aitiqaad pukhta ho gaey ( iske baad halal w haram ke ehkaam utrey , agar kahin shuru shuru' hi mein ye utartaa ke sharab na peenaa to log kehtey ham to kabhi sharab peenaa nahi chhodengey . agar shuru hi mein ye utartaa ke zina na karo to log kehtey ham to zina nahi chhodengey iske bajaey Makka mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par us waqt jab main bachchii thi aur khelaa karti thi ye aayat nazil huii بل الساعة موعدهم والساعة أدهى وأمر lekin sura al-Baqara aur sura Nisa us waqt nazil huin , jab main (Madina mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas thi. bayan kya ke phir unhon-ne us iraaqii ke liye apna musahaf nikala aur har sura ki aayatein ki tafseel likhwaaii ."
4994,"sura banii-Israaeel, sura Kahaf , sura Maryam , sura Taaha aur sura anbiya ke mutaalliq batlaya ke ye panchon soortein awwal darja ki Faseeh soortein hain aur meri yad ki hui hain."
4995,maine sura ( سبح اسم ربك الأعلى‏ ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Madina Munawra aaney se pahley hi seekh li thi.
4996,"main un judwaan Suraton ko janta hun jinhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har rakaat mein 2-2 padhtey they phir Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) majlis se khadey ho gaey (aur apne ghar) chaley gaey. Alqama bhi aap ke sath andar gaey. jab Alqama (Raziallahu anhu) bahar nikley to ham ne unse unhiin Suraton ke mutaalliq poochha. unhon-ne kaha ye shuru mufassal ki bees soortein hain, unki aakhiri soortein wo hain jinki awwal main ( حم ( hai. ( حم Dukhan (aur ( عم يتساءلون‏) bhi un hi mein se hain."
4997,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khair khairat karne mein sabse zyada data they aur Ramazan mein aap ki sakhawat ki to koi had hi nahi thi kyonke Ramazan ke mahinon mein Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aap se aa kar har raat miltey they yahan tak ke Ramazan ka mahina khatm ho jata wo un raaton main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Quran Majeed ka daurah kya kartey they. jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aap se miltey to us zamane main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tez hawa se bhi badh kar data (sakhii) ho jatey they.
4998,Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath har saal aik martaba Quran Majeed ka daurah kya kartey they lekin jis saal Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui usmein unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath 2 martaba daurah kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har saal das din ka aetikaf kya kartey they lekin jis saal aap ki wafat hui us saal aap ne bees din ka aetikaf kya.
4999,"Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-al-Aas ne Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr kya aur kaha ke us waqt se unki mohabbat mere dil mein ghar kar gaee hai jab se maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Quran Majeed ko char ashaab se hasil karo jo Abdullah-bin-Masood , Saalim, Muaz aur Ubai-bin-Kab hain."
5000,Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein khutba diya aur kaha ke Allah ki qism maine kuchh uper 70 soortein khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban Mubarak se sun kar hasil ki hain. Allah ki qism Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ko ye baat achi tarah malum hai ke main un sabse zyada Quran Majeed ka jaanney wala hun halanke main unse behtar nahi hun. Shaqiq ne bayan kya ke phir main majlis mein betha taake sahaba ki raey sun sakun ke wo kya kehtey hain lekin maine kisi se is baat ki tardeed nahi suni.
5001,ham teiswin mein they ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne sura Yusuf padhi to aik shakhs bola ke is tarah nahi nazil hui thi. ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney is sura ki tilawat ki thi aur aap ne meri qirat ki tahseen farmai thi. unhon-ne mehsus kya ke is moa'tariz ke munh se sharab ki badboo aa rahi hai farmaya ke Allah ki kitab ke mutaalliq jhoota bayan aur sharab peenaa jaisey gunah aik sath karta hai. phir unhon-ne is par had jari kara di.
5002,"ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, us Allah ki qism jiske siwa aur koi maabood nahi kitabullah ki jo sura bhi nazil hui hai iske mutaalliq main janta hun ke kahan nazil hui aur kitabullah ki jo aayat bhi nazil hui iske mutaalliq main janta hun ke kis ke barey mein nazil hui, aur agar mujhey khabar ho jaey ke koi shakhs mujh se zyada kitabullah ka jaanney wala hai aur oont hi uske paas mujhey pahuncha saktey hain (yani unka ghar bahut door hai) tab bhi main safar karke uske paas ja kar us se us ilm ko hasil karunga ."
5003,"maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein Quran ko kin logon ne jama kya tha, unhon-ne batlaya ke char sahaabiyon ne, ye charon qabila Ansar se hain. Uabii-bin-Ka'b, Muaz-bin-Jabal , Zaid-bin-Saabit aur Abu-Zaid . is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Fazal ne Husain bin waaqid se ki hai. unse Samama ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne."
5004,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat tak Quran Majeed ko char sahaabiyon ke siwa aur kisi ne jama nahi kya tha. abu-Darda , Muaz-bin-Jabal , Zaid-bin-Saabit aur Abu-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) . Anas ne kaha ke Abu-Zaid ke waaris ham huey hain."
5005,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Ubai-bin-Kab ham mein sabse achchhey qaari hain lekin Ubaii jahan ghalati kartey hain usko ham chhod detey hain (wo kuchh mansukh tilawat aayaton ko bhi padhtey hain) aur kehtey hain ke maine to is aayat ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh Mubarak se suna hai, main kisi ke kehney se usey chhodney wala nahi aur Allah ne khud farmaya hai ما ننسخ من آية أو ننسأها نأت بخير منها أو مثلها‏ ke ''ham jab kisi aayat ko mansukh kar detey hain phir ya to usey bhulaa detey hain ya us se behtar latey hain.''"
5006,"mein Namaz mein mashghool tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bulaya isliye main koi jawab nahi de sakaa, phir maine (aap ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar) arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main Namaz padh raha tha. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya Allah Taala ne tumhen hukm nahi farmaya hai) استجيبوا لله وللرسول إذا دعاكم‏ (ke ''Allah ke rasool jab tumhen pukaarein to unki pukar par fauran Allah ke rasool ke liye labbaik kaha karo.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya masjid se nikalney se pahley Quran ki sabse badi sura main tumhen kyon na sikhaa dun. phir aap ne mera hath pakad liya aur jab ham masjid se bahar nikalney lagey to maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne abhi farmaya tha ke masjid ke bahar nikalney se pahley aap mujhey Quran ki sabse badi sura bataaengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, wo sura ( الحمد لله رب العالمين ( hai yahi wo saat (7) aayatein hain jo (har Namaz mein) baar-baar padhi jati hain aur yahi wo Quran azeem hai jo mujhey diya gaya hai."
5007,"ham aik fauji safar mein they (raat mein) ham ne aik qabeele ke nazdeek padao kya. phir aik londi aai aur kaha ke qabeele ke sardaar ko bichho ne kaat liya hai aur hamarey qabeeley ke mard maujood nahi hain, kya tum mein koi bichho ka jhaad phoonk karne wala hai? aik sahabi ( khud abu-Saeed ( uske sath khadey ho gaey, ham ko malum tha ke wo jhaad-phoonk nahi jantey lekin unhon-ne qabeele ke sardaar ko jhaada to usey sihat ho gaee. us ne uske shukraaney mein tees bakriyan dene ka hukm diya aur hamein doodh pilaayaa. jab wo jhaad-phoonk karke wapas aaey to ham ne unse puchha kya tum waqei koi mantr jantey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi maine to sirf sura Fatiha padh kar is par dam kar diya tha. ham ne kaha ke achchha jab tak ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uske mutaalliq na poochh lein un bakriyon ke barey main apni taraf se kuchh na kaho. chunanche ham ne Madina pahunch kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhon-ne kaisey jana ke sura Fatiha mantr bhi hai. (jaao ye maal halal hai) usey taqseem kar lo aur is mein mera bhi hissey lagaanaa aur Mamar ne bayan kya ham se Abdul-Waris bin Saeed ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Hisham bin Hassan ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Muhammad-bin Sirin ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Mabad bin Sirin ne bayan kya aur unse Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne yahi waqia bayan kya."
5008,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (sura al-Baqara mein se) jisne bhi 2 aakhiri aayatein padhin. (doosri sanad agli hadis dekhein).
5009,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne sura al-Baqara ki 2 aakhiri aayatein raat mein padh lein wo usey har aafat se bachaney ke liye kafi ho jaeyngi .
5010,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey sadqa fitr ki hifazat par muqarrar farmaya, phir aik shakhs aaya aur donon hathon se ( khajoorein ( sametney laga. maine usey pakad liya aur kaha ke main tujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh karunga . phir unhon-ne ye pura qissa bayan kya ( mufassal hadis is se pahley kitaabul-wakaala mein guzar chuki hai) (jo sadqa fitr churaaney aaya tha) usne kaha ke jab tum raat ko apne bistar par soney ke liye jao to aayatal-kursii padh liya karo, phir subah tak Allah Taala ki taraf se tumhari hifazat karne wala aik farishta muqarrar ho jaeyga aur shaitan tumharey paas bhi na aa sakega. (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye baat aap se bayan ki to ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya us ne tumhen ye theek baat batai hai agarche wo bada jhoota hai, wo shaitan tha."
5011,aik sahabi ( Usaid-bin-Huzair ( sura Kahaf padh rahe they. unke aik taraf aik ghoda 2 rasson se bandhaa hua tha. us waqt aik abr uper se aaya aur nazdeek se nazdeek tar honey laga. unka ghoda uski wjah se bidakney laga. phir subah ke waqt wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se iska zikr kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo ( abr ka tukda ( ) سكينة ( tha jo Quran ki tilawat ki wjah se utra tha.
5012,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko aik safar mein ja rahe they. umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath they. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kuchh poochha. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iska koi jawab na diya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne phir puchha aap ne phir koi jawab nahi diya. teesri martaba phir puchha aur jab is martaba bhi koi jawab nahi diya to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apne aapko) kaha teri maan tujh par roey tu ney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se teen martaba aajizii se sawal kya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi martaba bhi jawab nahi diya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir maine apni ontni ko daudaayaa aur logon se aagey ho gaya (aap ke barabar chalnaa chhod diyaa) mujhey khof tha ke kahin us harkat par mere barey mein koi aayat nazil na ho jaey abhi thoda hi waqt guzra tha ke maine aik pukarney waley ko suna jo pukar raha tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine sochaa mujhey to khof tha hi ke mere barey mein kuchh wahi nazil hogi. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur maine aapko salam kya (salaam ke jawab ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Umar! aaj raat mujh par aisi sura nazil hui hai jo mujhey un sab chizon se zyada pasand hai jin par suraj nikalta hai. phir aap ne sura ( إنا فتحنا لك فتحا مبينا‏ ( ki tilawat farmai .
5013,aik sahabi (khud abu-Saeed khudrii) ne aik doosrey sahabi (Qataada bin Nauman (rz)) apne maan jaey bhai ko dekha ke wo raat ko sura ( قل هو الله أحد‏ ( baar-baar padh rahe hain. subah hui to wo sahabi (abu-Saeed (rz)) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya maano unhon-ne samjha ke usmein koi bada sawab na hoga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! ye sura Quran Majeed ke aik tehai hissey ke barabar hai.
5014,mujhey mere bhai Qatada bin Nauman (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke aik sahabi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein sehrii ke waqt se khadey ( قل هو الله أحد‏ ( padhtey rahe. unke siwa aur kuchh nahi padhtey they. phir jab subah hui to doosrey sahabi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey ( baqi hissey ( pichhli hadis ki tarah bayan kya.
5015,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba se farmaya ke kya tum mein se kisi ke liye ye mumkin nahi ke Quran ka aik tehai hissey aik raat mein padha karey? sahaba ko ye amal bada mushkil malum hua aur unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham mein se kon uski taqat rakhta hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke) الواحد الصمد ( (yani ( قل هو الله أحد‏ ( Quran Majeed ka aik tehai hissey hai. Muhammad-bin Yusuf farbarii ne bayan kya ke maine abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke kaatib abu-Jafar Muhammad-bin abi Hatim se suna, wo kehtey they ke imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha Ibrahim Nakhai ki riwayat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se munqata' hai) Ibrahim ne abu-Saeed se nahi suna ( lekin Suhak mashriqii ki riwayat abu-Saeed se muttasil hai."
5016,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bimar padtey to muawwizaat ki soortein padh kar usey apne uper dam kartey (is tarah ke hawa ke sath kuchh thook bhi nikaltaa) phir jab (marzul-maut mein) aap ki takleef badh gaee to main un Suraton ko padh kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hathon se barkat ki ummeed mein aap ke jism par pherti thi.
5017,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har raat jab bistar par aaraam farmatey to apni donon hatheliyon ko mila kar) قل هو الله أحد ( , Mina ( قل أعوذ برب Falaq (aur ( قل أعوذ برب Naas ( ) teenon soortein mukammal ( padh kar un par phoonktey aur phir donon hatheliyon ko jahan tak mumkin hota apne jism par phertey they. pahley sar aur chehra par hath phertey aur samney ke badan par. ye amal Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) teen baar kartey they."
5018,"raat ke waqt wo sura al-Baqara ki tilawat kar rahe they aur unka ghoda unke paas hi bandhaa hua tha. itney mein ghoda bidakney laga to unhon-ne tilawat band kar di to ghoda bhi ruk gaya. phir unhon-ne tilawat shuru ki to ghoda phir bidakney laga. is martaba bhi jab unhon-ne tilawat band ki to ghoda bhi khamosh ho gaya. teesri martaba unhon-ne tilawat shuru ki to phir ghoda bidkaa . unke betey Yahya chunkey ghodey ke qareeb hi they isliye us dar se ke kahin unhein koi takleef na pahunch jaey. unhon-ne tilawat band kar di aur bachchey ko wahan se hata diya phir uper nazar uthai to kuchh na dikhai diya. subah ke waqt ye waqia unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ibne- Huzer ! tum padhtey rahtey tilawat band na kartey (to behtar tha) unhon-ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! mujhey dar laga ke kahin ghoda mere bachchey Yahya ko na kuchal daaley, wo us se bahut qareeb tha. maine sar uper uthaya aur phir Yahya ki taraf gaya. phir maine aasman ki taraf sar uthaya to aik chhatrii si nazar aai jis mein roshan charagh they. phir jab main dobara bahar aaya to maine usey nahi dekha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen malum bhi hai wo kya cheez thi? Usaid ne arz kya ke nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo Farishtey they tumhari awaz sunney ke liye qareeb ho rahe they agar tum raat bhar padhtey rahtey to subah tak aur log bhi unhein dekhtey wo logon se chhiptey nahi. aur ibne-al-haad ne bayan kya, kaha mujh se ye hadis Abdullah-bin Khabbaab ne bayan ki, unse Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) ne."
5019,main aur Shaddad bin Maaqil Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey. Shaddad bin Maaqil ne unse puchha kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is Quran ke siwa koi aur bhi Quran chhoda tha. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( wahi matloo ( jo kuchh bhi chhodi hai wo sab ki sab un 2 gatton ke darmyan saheefae mein mehfooz hai Abdul-Azeez bin rafeea' kehtey hain ke ham Muhammad-bin-Haneefa ki khidmat mein bhi hazir huey aur unse bhi puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo bhi wahi matloo chhodi wo sab 2 daftiyon ke darmyan ( Quran Majeed ki shakl mein) mehfooz hai.
5020,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski ( momin ki) misal jo Quran ki tilawat karta hai sangtarey ki si hai jiska maza bhi lazeez hota hai aur jiski khushbu bhi behtreen hoti hai aur jo momin Quran ki tilawat nahi karta uski misal khajoor ki si hai uska maza to umda hota hai lekin usmein khushbu nahi hoti aur us badkaar (munaafiq) ki misal jo Quran ki tilawat karta hai Rehana ki si hai ke uski khushbu to achi hoti lekin maza kadwaa hota hai aur us badkaar ki misal jo Quran ki tilawat bhi nahi karta indraayan ki si hai jiska maza bhi kadwaa hota hai aur is mein koi khushbu bhi nahi hoti.
5021,"maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke musalmaanon! guzri ummaton ki umaron ke muqaabla mein tumhari umr aisi hai jaisey Asr se suraj doobney tak ka waqt hota hai aur tumhari aur yahood w nasara ki misal aisi hai ke kisi shakhs ne kuchh mazdoor kaam par lagaey aur unse kaha ke aik qirat mazdoorii par mera kaam subah se do-pahar tak kon karega? ye kaam yahudiyon ne kya. phir usne kaha ke ab mera kaam aadhey din se Asr tak (eik hi qirat mazdoorii par) kon karega? ye kaam nasara ne kya. phir tum ne Asr se maghrib tak 2-2 qirat mazdoorii par kaam kya. yahood w nasara qiyamat ke din kahengey ham ne kaam zyada kya lekin mazdoorii kam paai ? Allah Taala farmaeyga kya tumhara kuchh haq maara gaya? wo kahengey ke nahi. phir Allah Taala farmaeyga ke phir ye mera Fazal hai, main jisey chaahoon aur jitna chaahoon ata karun."
5022,maine Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya : kya Nabi Karim ne koi wasiiyat farmai thi? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. maine arz kya : phir logon par wasiiyat kaisey farz ki gaee ke musalmanon ko to wasiiyat ka hukm hai aur khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi wasiiyat nahi farmai. unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kitabullah ko mazbootii se thaamey rehney ki wasiiyat farmai thi.
5023,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ne koi cheez itni tawajjoh se nahi suni jitni tawajjoh se us ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka Quran behtreen awaz ke sath padhtey huey suna hai. abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ka aik dost abdul-hameed bin Abdur-Rehman kehta tha ke is hadis main ( يتغنى بالقرآن ( se ye murad hai ke achi awaz se usey pukar kar padhey.
5024,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne koi cheez tawajjoh se nahi suni jitni tawajjoh se apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko behtreen awaz ke sath Quran Majeed padhtey suna hai. Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha ( يتغنى بالقرآن ( se murad hai ke Quran par qanaa'at kare.
5025,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, rashk to bas 2 hi aadmiyon par ho sakta hai aik to is par jisey Allah ne Quran Majeed ka ilm diya aur wo uske sath raat ki ghadiyon mein khada ho kar Namaz padhta raha aur doosra aadmi wo jisey Allah Taala ne maal diya aur wo usey mohtajon par raat din khairat karta raha."
5026,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke rashk to bas 2 hi aadmiyon par hona chahiye aik is par jisey Allah Taala ne Quran ka ilm diya aur wo raat din uski tilawat karta rehta hai ke uska padosi sun kar keh uthey ke kash! mujhey bhi us jaisa ilm Quran hota aur main bhi uski tarah amal karta aur wo doosra jisey Allah ne maal diya aur wo usey haq ke liye lita raha hai) usko dekh kar) doosra shakhs keh uthtaa hai ke kash! mere paas bhi iske jitna maal hota aur main bhi uski tarah kharch karta.
5027,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein sabse behtar wo hai jo Quran Majeed padhey aur padhaaey. Sad bin Ubeda ne bayan kya ke abu-Abdur-Rehman Salma ne logon ko Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamane khilafat se Hajjaj-bin-Yosuf ke Iraq ke governer honey tak Quran Majeed ki taleem di. wo kaha kartey they ke yahi hadis hai jisne mujhey is jagah (Qur'aan Majeed padhaaney ke liye) bitha rakha hai.
5028,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum sab mein behtar wo hai jo Quran Majeed padhey aur padhaaey .
5029,aik khatun Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha ke unhon-ne apne aapko Allah aur uske rasool (ki raza (ke liye hiba kar diya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab mujhey aurton se nikah ki koi haajat nahi hai. aik sahib ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! unka nikah mujh se kar dein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir unhein (mahar mein) aik kapda la kar de do. unhon-ne arz kya ke mujhey to ye bhi muyassar nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir unhein kuchh to 2 aik lohey ki anguthi hi sahii. wo is par bahut pareshan huey (kyonke unke paas ye bhi na thi). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha tum ko Quran kitna yad hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke falan-falan soortein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir maine tumhara unse Quran ki un Suraton par nikah kya jo tumhen yad hain.
5030,"aik khatun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! main aap ki khidmat main apne aapko hiba karne ke liye aai hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki taraf nazar utha kar dekha aur phir nazar neechi kar li aur sar jhukaa liya. jab us khatun ne dekha ke unke barey mein koi faisla Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi farmaya to wo baith gaee. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se aik sahib uthey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! agar aapko unki zarurat nahi hai to mere sath unka nikah kar dein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya tumharey paas kuchh ( mehar ke liye) bhi hai. unhon-ne arz kya nahi ya Rasulullah , Allah ki qasam! to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne ghar jao aur dekho shayad koi cheez miley, wo sahib gaey aur wapas aagey aur arz kya nahi, Allah ki qism ! ya Rasulullah ! mujhey wahan koi cheez nahi mili . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir dekh lo aik lohey ki anguthi hi sahii . wo sahib gaey aur phir wapas aagey aur arz kya nahi Allah ki qism , ya Rasulullah ! lohey ki aik anguthi bhi mujhey nahi milii. albatta ye aik tehband mere paas hai. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke unke paas koi chadar bhi (odhney ke liye) nahi thi. us sahabi ne kaha ke khatun ko usmein se aadha phaad kar de dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey us tehband ka wo kya karegii. agar tum usey pahntey ho to iske qaabil nahi rehta aur agar wo pahantii hai to tumharey qaabil nahi. phir wo sahib baith gaey kafi der tak baithey rehney ke baad uthey . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein jatey huey dekha to bulwaya . jab wo hazir huey to aap ne malum farmaya ke tumhen Quran Majeed kitna yad hai? unhon-ne batlaya ke fulaan, fulaan, falan soortein mujhey yad hain. unhon-ne unke naam ginaaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya tum unhein zabani padh letey ho? arz kya ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jao tumhen Quran Majeed ki jo soortein yad hain unke badley mein maine usey tumharey nikah mein de diya."
5031,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Hafiz Quran ki misal rassii se bandhey huey oont ke Malik jaisi hai aur wo uski nigrani rakhega to wo usey rok sakega warna wo rassii tudwa kar bhag jaeyga
5032,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bahut bura hai kisi shakhs ka ye kehna ke main falan-falan aayat bhool gaya balke yun (kahnaa chahiye (ke mujhey bhulaa diya gaya aur Quran Majeed ka padhna jari rakho kyonke insanon ke dilon se door ho janey mein wo oont ke bhaagney se bhi badh kar hai. ham se Usman bin abi Sheba ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Jarir bin abdul-hameed ne, aur unse Mansoor bin Motamir ne pichhli hadis ki tarah Muhammad-bin ar-ara ke sath usko Bishr bin-Abdullah ne bhi Abdullah-bin-Mubarak se, unhon-ne Shoba se riwayat kya hai aur Muhammad-bin ar-ara ke sath usko ibne-Juraij ne bhi Abda se, unhon-ne Shaqiq se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Masood se aisa hi riwayat kya hai."
5033,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Quran Majeed ka padhtey rehna lazim pakad lo ''us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai wo oont ke apni rassii tudwa kar bhag janey se zyada tezi se bhaagta hai.
5034,"mujhey Abu-Ayaas ne khabar di, kaha ke maine Abdullaah-bin-mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko fateh Makka ke din dekha ke aap sawari par sura fateh ki tilawat farma rahe they."
5035,jin Suraton ko tum mufassal kehtey ho wo sab mohkam hain. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to meri umr das saal ki thi aur maine mohkam soortein sab padh li thin.
5036,"maine mohkam soortein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein sab yad kar li thin, maine puchha ke mohkam soortein kon si hain? kaha ke mufassal."
5037,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko masjid mein Quran padhtey suna to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah is par raham karey, usne mujhey falan sura ki falan-falan aayatein yad dila dein."
5038,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sahib ko raat ke waqt aik sura padhtey huey suna to farmaya ke Allah Taala us shakhs par raham karey, usne mujhey falan aayatein yad dila diin jo mujhey falan-falan Suraton mein se bhulaa di gaee thin."
5039,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi ke liye ye munasib nahi ke ye kahey ke main falan-falan aayatein bhool gaya balke usey (yoon kehna chaahiye) ke main falan-falan aayaton ko bhala diya gaya.
5040,"mujh se Ibrahim ne bayan kya, unse Alqama aur Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed ne aur unse Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sura al-Baqara ke aakhir ki 2 aayaton ko jo shakhs raat mein padh lega wo uske liye kafi hongii."
5041,maine Hisham bin Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein sura furqan padhtey suna. main unki qirat ko ghaur se sunney laga to malum hua ke wo aisey bahut se tariqon mein tilawat kar rahe they jinhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein nahi sikhaya tha. mumkin tha ke main Namaz hi mein unka sar pakad leta lekin maine intizar kya aur jab unhon-ne salam phera to maine unke galey mein chadar lapet di aur puchha ye soortein jinhein abhi abhii tumhen padhtey huey maine suna hai tumhen kis ne sikhai hain? unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey is tarah un Suraton ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sikhaya hai. maine kaha ke tum jhoot bol rahe ho. khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bhi ye soortein padhai hain jo maine tum se sunein . main unhein kheenchtey huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! maine khud suna ke ye shakhs sura furqan aisi qirat se padh raha tha. jiski taleem aap ne hamein nahi di hai aap mujhey bhi sura furqan padha chukey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Hisham ! padh kar sunao. unhon-ne isi tarah uski qirat ki jis tarah mein unse sun chuka tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke isi tarah ye sura nazil hui hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Umar! ab tum padho. maine bhi isi tarah qirat ki jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey sikhaya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke isi tarah ye sura nazil hui thi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Quran Majeed saat (7) qism ki qiraton par nazil hua hai bas tumharey liye jo aasan ho iske mutabiq padho.
5042,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik qaari ko raat ke waqt masjid mein Quran Majeed padhtey huey suna to farmaya ke Allah us aadmi par raham karey usne mujhey falan-falan aayatein yad dila diin jinhein maine falan-falan Suraton mein se chhod rakha tha.
5043,ham unki khidmat mein subah sawerey hazir huey. haaziriin mein se aik sahib ne kaha ke raat maine (tamaam) mufassal soortein padh daaliin. is par Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) boley jaisey ashaar jaldi-jaldi padhtey hain tum ne waisey hi padh li hogi. ham se qirat suni hai aur mujhey wo jod wali soortein bhi yad hain jinko mila kar namazon mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) padha kartey they. ye atthaara soortein mufassal ki hain aur wo 2 soortein jinke shuru main ( حم‏ ( hai.
5044,"Allah Taala ke farmaan ( لا تحرك به لسانك لتعجل به ) '' aap Quran ko jaldi jaldii leney ke liye is par zaban ko na hilaayaa karein.'' bayan kya ke jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) wahi lekar nazil hotey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni zaban aur hont hilaayaa kartey they. uski wjah se aap ke liye wahi yad karne mein bahut baar padta tha aur ye aap ke chehrey se bhi zahir ho jata tha. isliye Allah Taala ne ye aayat jo sura ( لا أقسم بيوم القيامة‏ ( mein hai, nazil ki ke aap Quran ko jaldi jaldii leney ke liye is par zaban ko na hilaayaa karein ye to hamarey zimme hai iska jama karna aur iska padhwaanaa to jab ham usey padhney lagein to aap iske peechhey peechhey padha karein phir aap ki zaban se uski tafseer bayan kara dena bhi hamarey zimme hai.'' rawi ne bayan kya ke phir jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aatey to aap sar jhukaa letey aur jab wapas jatey to padhtey jaisa ke Allah ne aap se yad karwaaney ka wada kya tha ke terey dil mein jama dena usko padha dena hamara kaam hai phir aap iske muwafiq padhtey ."
5045,maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tilawat Quran Majeed ke mutaalliq sawal kya to unhon-ne batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un alfaz ko kheench kar padhtey they jin mein mudd hota tha.
5046,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qirat kaisi thi? unhon-ne bayan kya ke mudd ke saath. phir aap ne ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( padha aur kaha ke) بسم الله ( (main Allah ki Lam ( ko mudd ke sath padhtey ( الرحمن ( (main meem) ko mudd ke sath padhtey aur) الرحيم‏ .) (main حاء ko) mudd ke sath padhtey .
5047,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni ontni ya oont par Sawar ho kar tilawat kar rahe they sawari chal rahi thi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sura fateh padh rahe they ya ( rawi ne ye bayan kya ke) sura fateh mein se padh rahe they narmii aur aahisatagi ke sath qirat kar rahe they aur awaz ko halaq mein dohraatey they.
5048,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey abu-Moosa! tujhey Dawud (Alaihissalam) jaisi behtreen awaz ata ki gaee hai.''
5049,mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey Quran Majeed padh kar sunao. maine arz kya main aapko Quran sunaun aap par to Quran nazil hota hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main Quran Majeed doosrey se sunnaa mahboob rakhta hun.
5050,"mujh se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey Quran padh kar sunao. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main aapko padh kar sunaun, aap par to Quran Majeed nazil hota hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan sunao. chunanche maine sura Nisa padhi jab main aayat فكيف إذا جئنا من كل أمة بشهيد وجئنا بك على هؤلاء شهيدا par pahuncha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab bas karo. maine aap ki taraf dekha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon se aansu jari they."
5051,"Namaz mein kitna Quran padhna kafi ho sakta hai. phir maine dekha ke aik sura mein teen aayaton se kam nahi hai. isliye maine ye raey qaaim ki ke kisi ke liye teen aayaton se kam padhna munasib nahi. Ali al-Madeenii ne bayan kya ke ham se Sufiyan Sory ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko Mansoor ne khabar di, unhein Ibrahim ne, unhein Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed ne, unhein Alqama ne khabar di aur unhein Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne (alqama ne bayan kya ke) maine unse mulaqat ki to wo Baitullah ka tawaaf kar rahe they. unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr kya (ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha) ke jisne sura al-Baqara ke aakhiri ki 2 aayatein raat mein padh lin wo uske liye kafi hain."
5052,"mere walid Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mera nikah aik sharif khandan ki aurat (umme-Muhammad binte- mahmiya) se kar diya tha aur hamesha uski khabar-geerii kartey rahtey they aur unse baar-baar uske shauhar (yani khud un) ke mutaalliq poochhtey rahtey they. meri biwi kehti ke bahut achchha mard hai. albatta jab se main unke nikah mein aai hun unhon-ne ab tak hamarey bistar par qadam bhi nahi rakha na mere kapdey mein kabhi hath dala. jab bahut din isi tarah ho gaey to walid sahib ne majbur ho kar iska tazkira Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujh se uski mulaqat karaao. chunanche main iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mila. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke roza kis tarah rakhtey ho. maine arz kya ke rozaana. phir malum farmaya Quran Majeed kis tarah khatm kartey ho? maine arz kya har raat. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har mahiney mein teen din rozey rakho aur Quran aik mahiney mein khatm karo. bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mujhey is se zyada ki taqat hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir bila rozey ke raho aur aik din rozey se. maine arz kya mujhey us se bhi zyada ki taqat hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir wo roza rakho jo sabse afzal hai, yani Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza , aik din roza rakho aur aik din iftaar karo aur Quran Majeed saat (7) din mein khatm karo. Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they kash! maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki rukhsat qabool kar li hoti kyonke ab main boodha aur kamzor ho gaya hun. Hajjaj ne kaha ke aap apne ghar ke kisi aadmi ko Quran Majeed ka saatwan hissey yani aik manzil din mein suna detey they. jitna Quran Majeed aap raat ke waqt padhtey usey pahley din mein suna rakhtey taake raat ke waqt aasani se padh sakein aur jab ( quwwat khatm ho jati aur nidhaal ho jatey aur) quwwat hasil karna chahtey to kai-kai din roza na rakhtey kyonke aapko ye pasand nahi tha ke jis cheez ka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aagey wada kar liya hai (eik din roza rakhna aik din iftaar karna ( usmein se kuchh bhi chhodein. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) kehtey hain ke kuchh rawiyon ne teen din main aur kuchh ne panch din mein. lekin aksar ne saat (7) raaton mein khatm ki hadis riwayat ki hai."
5053,mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke Quran Majeed tum kitney din mein khatm kar letey ho?
5054,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke har mahiney mein Quran ka aik hissey khatm kya karo maine arz kya mujh ko to zyada padhney ki taqat hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha saat (7) raaton mein khatm kya karo. us se zyada mat padh.
5055,"is hadis ka kuchh tukda Aamash ne Ibrahim se khud suna hai aur kuchh tukda Amr-bin-Murra sey, unhoney Ibrahim se suna hai ke mujh se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, (dusri sanad ( ham se Musaddad ne bayan kyaa, kaha ham se Yahya Qataan ney, un se Sufiyan saurii ney, un se Aamash ney, un se Ibrahim ney, un se Ubeda salmaanii ne aur un se Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney. Aamash ne bayan kya ke maine is hadis ka aik tukda to khud Ibrahim se suna aur aik tukda is hadis ka mujh se Amr-bin-Murra ne naql kyaa, un se Ibrahim ney, un se unke walid ne un se abu-Zuha ne aur un se Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mere samney Quran Majeed ki tilawat karo. maine arz kya aanhazrat ke samney main kya tilawat karun aap par too Quran Majeed nazil hi hota hai. huzoor akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main chahta hun ke kisi aur se sunoon. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir maine sura Nisa padhi aur jab main aayat «فَكَيْفَ إِذَا جِئْنَا مِنْ كُلِّ أُمَّةٍ بِشَهِيدٍ، وَجِئْنَا بِكَ عَلَى هَؤُلاَءِ شَهِيدًا» par pahuncha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke thahar jao (aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( «کف» farmaya ya «امسک» rawi ko shak hai. maine dekha ke aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon se aansu bah rahey they."
5056,mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey Quran Majeed padh kar sunao. maine arz kya : kya main sunaun? aap par to Quran Majeed nazil hota hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main kisi se sunnaa mahboob rakhta hun.
5057,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aakhiri zamane mein aik qaum paida hogi naujawaanon aur kam aqlon ki. ye log aisa behtreen kalam padhengey jo behtreen khalq ka (paighambar ka ( hai ya aisa kalam padhengey jo sarey khalq ke kalaamon se afzal hai. (yani hadis ya aayat padhengey us se sanad laaengey) lekin Islam se wo is tarah nikal jaeinge jaisey teer shikar ko paar karke nikal jata hai unka eman unke halaq se nichey nahi utrega tum unhein jahan bhi paogey qatl kar do. kyonke unka qatl qiyamat mein us shakhs ke liye baaise-ajr hoga jo unhein qatl kar dega."
5058,"tum mein aik qaum aisi paida hogi ke tum apni Namaz ko unki Namaz ke muqable mein haqeer samjhogey, unke rozon ke muqable main tumhen apne rozey aur unke amal ke muqaabla main tumhen apna amal haqeer nazar aayega aur wo Quran Majeed ki tilawat bhi karengey lekin Quran Majeed unke halaq se nichey nahi utrega . Deen se wo is tarah nikal jaeinge jaisey teer shikar ko paar kartey huey nikal jata hai aur wo bhi itni safaaii ke sath (ke teer chalaney wala ( teer ke phal mein dekhta hai to usmein bhi) shikar ke khoon wghaira ka ( koi asar nazar nahi aataa. us se uper dekhta hai wahan bhi kuchh nazar nahi aataa. teer ke par ko dekhta hai aur wahan bhi kuchh nazar nahi aataa. bas usey fal mein kuchh shuba guzarta hai."
5059,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us momin ki misal jo Quran Majeed padhta hai aur is par amal bhi karta hai methey leemoon ki si hai jiska mazaa bhi lazzat daar aur khushbu bhi achi aur wo momin jo Quran padhta to nahi lekin is par amal karta hai uski misal khajoor ki hai jiska maza to umda hai lekin khushbu ke baghair aur us munafiq ki misal jo Quran padhta hai reaihaan ki si hai jiski khushbu to achi hoti hai lekin mazaa kadwaa hota hai aur us munafiq ki misal jo Quran bhi nahi padhta indraayan ke phal ki si hai jiska maza bhi kadwaa hota hai) rawi ko shak hai) ke lafz ( mar ( hai ya ( khabees (aur uski bo bhi kharaab hoti hai.
5060,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Quran Majeed us waqt tak padho jab tak usmein dil lagey, jab ji uchaat honey lagey to padhna band kar do."
5061,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is Quran ko jab hi tak padho jab tak tumharey dil miley juley ya lagey rahen. jab ikhtilaf aur jhagdaa karne lago to uth khadey ho. ( Quran Majeed padhna moquf kar do ( salam ke sath us hadis ko Haris bin Ubaid aur Saeed bin Zaid ne bhi abu-Imran Jawni se riwayat kya aur Hammaad-bin-Salma aur Aban ne usko marfooan nahi balke mauqoofan riwayat kya hai aur ghandar Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne bhi Shoba se, unhon-ne abu-Imran se yun riwayat kya ke maine Jundub se suna, wo kehtey they. ( lekin mauqoofan riwayat kya) aur Abdullah-bin Aun ne usko abu-Imran se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Samit se, unhon-ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se unka qaul riwayat kya (marfooan nahi kya (aur Jundub ki riwayat zyada sahi hai."
5062,"Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik sahib (Uabii-bin-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu)) ko aik aayat padhtey suna, wahi aayat unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske khilaf suni thi. (ibn-Mas'ood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) phir maine unka hath pakda aur unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum donon sahi ho (is liye apne apney taur par padho) (Shoba kehtey hain ke) mera ghalib guman ye hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya ke) ikhtilaf w nazaa' na kya karo) kyonke tum se pahley ki ummaton ne ikhtilaf kya aur usi wjah se Allah Taala ne unhein halaak kar diya."
